<HEADLINE>
`INSIDER' NAMED BEST FILM
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Glenn Whipp is the Daily News film writer.) 
(EDITORS: Daily News Staff Writers David Kronke, Bob Strauss and
Glenn Whipp voted in the balloting. The awards will be handed out
at a dinner in mid-January.) 
(Moving in the ``a'' national news file, the ``e'' entertainment
news file and in the ``n'' California news file.) 
By GLENN WHIPP  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ ``The Insider'' was named best film of the year by
the Los Angeles Film Critics Association, winning a total of four
