elections. By Steven Erlanger.
</P>
<P>
   ??????
</P>
<P>
   U.N.-ANNAN-ISRAEL (United Nations) _ Secretary-General Kofi
Annan is expected to deliver a speech Sunday night that amounts to
a strong and unambiguous call for better treatment of Israel at the
United Nations. By Barbara Crossette.
</P>
<P>
   BOSNIA-WARCRIMES (Washington) _ As NATO peacekeeping troops
enter their fifth year on patrol in Bosnia, dozens of Bosnians
accused of genocide, rape and other war crimes have not only eluded
capture, but are reported to live openly with little fear of
arrest. By Philip Shenon.
