<P>
   PANAMA-CANAL (Panama City, Panama) _ Preparations are underway
for the handover of the canal this week.
</P>
<P>
   EU-QUICKREACT (Paris) _ By deciding to equip itself to send up
to 60,000 troops to a crisis zone like Bosnia or Kosovo, the
European Union aims to become a strategic player on the world scene
that the United States and other countries will have to reckon
with. By Craig R. Whitney.
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA-CHECHNYA (Dateline TK) _ Developments in the fighting
between Russian troops and Islamic militants in the breakaway
republic. By Michael R. Gordon.
</P>
<P>
   Tentative:
</P>
