<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AA-`ACRONYMS-ANONYMOUS'-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
S.O.S. AAAAA: ASSN. OF ABSURD ACRONYMS AND ASININE ABBREVIATIONS  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Humor Editors)   (This quirky 600-word ``separate-buy'' article is from the current
(week beginning 11 DEC. 1999) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada except to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
