nose.
</P>
<P>
   Bush has sent a cease-and-desist letter to the site's creator,
Zack Exley, accusing him of using pictures ``borrowed'' from his
Web site.
</P>
<P>
   He has also complained to the Federal Election Commission (FEC)
that the site constitutes ``express advocacy,'' and violates the
