</P>
<P>
   To some in his party, ``odd'' would hardly be the word for it.
``Completely misguided'' might be better, or perhaps ``socialist
meddling in areas which government should leave alone.''
</P>
<P>
   Ridge is unapologetic. He believes in governmental activism. ``I
get to do the stuff below the radar screen that makes a real
