much.''
</P>
<P>
   He is also strongly pro-business. ``One of my biggest challenges
was to change the perception that Pennsylvania was not a good place
to do business,'' he says.
</P>
<P>
   Since he took over in the Republican landslide year of 1994, he
has reduced the business-tax burden by $3 billion, partly by
