<P>
   BRADLEY _ ORLANDO, Fla. _ A day after the Gore/Clinton
appearance at the Florida Democratic convention, Bradley comes to
the gathering playing his outsider game. So far it appears to be
clicking for him in Iowa and New Hampshire but Bradley has spent
little time in the Sunshine State. Will he win them over and cause
even further worry for Gore? (Crowley, Palm Beach Post). 20.
</P>
